job.body:
Total Vacancies:370


Name of the post:

  • Staff Nurse Grade A  

Description:

The Rajendra Institute of Medical Sciences issued a total of 370 vacancies for the posts of Staff Nurse Grade A. The online application for the posts of Staff Nurse Grade A  under Rajendra Institute of Medical Sciences shall start from 14.03.2021. The eligible candidates can apply for the online application before 30.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, for Staff Nurse Grade A mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The interested candidates after filling the application form, it is required to pay the application fee to complete the form submission process:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for the SC/ST is INR 150/-
  • The application fee for the rest of the candidates is INR 600/-
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 14.03.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 30.04.2021

Educational qualification required:

Candidates who are interested in Staff Nurse Grade A  should have the following qualification from a recognized University/boards with marks :

  • You must have a degree in BSc nursing to apply for the post of Staff Nurse Grade A  

Age limit criteria:

The interested candidates must have fallen in the age limit criteria provided by the Rajendra Institute of Medical Sciences is:

  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

How to apply for RIMS Ranchi Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of Rajendra Institute of Medical Sciences.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Staff Nurse Grade A.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
